   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Emergency Relief Packages to 4,750 Greek Families</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Today 63% of the Greek workforce is unemployed or poor. Despite the rhetoric, austerity measures and heavy taxation have had a devastating effect on daily life. 40% of small and medium sized businesses have shut down in the last 3 years. KID &amp; FAMILY is currently distributing AID, food &amp; basic essential supplies, directly to 4,750 homes to save them from diseases &amp; hunger. Our distributions ensure that families with young children existing in extreme poverty survive. We need your help to go on!</narrative>
  </description>
